{"tid":1171674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"26歲男突破中心天台鞋帶上吊亡","createTime":"2019-05-26T01:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T03:23:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":134,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"75563e61d8b7240fb5852075edb0bfb55f56fcac","tid":1171674,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T01:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.landvision.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/website/resize/buildings/004608/Breakthrough%20Centre%204.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landvision.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fwebsite%2Fresize%2Fbuildings%2F004608%2FBreakthrough%2520Centre%25204.JPG&h=8028d00c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油麻地一名26歲男子以鞋帶上吊，送院後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n現場為吳松街191號突破中心，昨晚（25日）11時41分，警方接獲上址保安報案稱，有人於大廈天台一鐵架以鞋帶上吊。消防接報到場將26歲薜姓男事主解下，薜昏迷被送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救，其後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方未於現場檢獲遺書，經初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，其死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288<br />\n<br />\n年輕人專線<br />\n<br />\n香港輔導及心理學會：WhatsApp熱線6218 1084 (提供英語及粵語專業輔導服務)<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：青少年生命專線 2382 0777<br />\n<br />\n賽馬會青少年網上輔導平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"https://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=9e77b38f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"9165dda2cbc6653e2124f9ec28d02fbcaca6affa","tid":1171674,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T01:23:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190526/s00001/1558833098948/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190526%2Fs00001%2F1558833098948%2F&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=aa94f4c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Fart